" dir="rtl">تَجْرِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">flowing</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن تَحْتِىٓ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">underneath me.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَفَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then do not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُبْصِرُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you see?</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>51<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
